  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "Raleigh International Nepal (RIN) has decided to implement the project in Kathmandu district especially Kathmandu metropolitan city namely Youth green Education and Entrepreneurship project focusing on mobilization of young people with campaign, Awareness on knowledge into behavior, sustainable consumption, segregation at household level, strong implementation in 5R (Reduce, Recycle, Repair, Refuse, Refer), Reduce/Reuse the use of plastic and consumers awareness, Carry own Fiber bags (Alternatives), contribute in implementation of existing law, subsidy on environmentally friendly goods, Increase concept of waste management in school curriculum , Take responsibility of waste created by the organization proper disposal, Management of Dumping/landfill Site, Dustbins and waste management near the supermarkets (by authorities), strong and regular monitoring by local authorities, producers of major consumer product should be overlooked by them (E.g. wai wai   Chaudhary Group) and reduce the use of plastic by them, Promoting Eco-Friendly startups, Spread Knowledge through groups, Family and Friends, Awareness campaign in social media, Cleanliness Campaign, Awareness of yourself and others, support active participation with increased collaboration in organization and Government, strong management of household waste and waste segregation and interconnection of waste and livelihood etc."
    },
    "ne": null
  },
